            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Caesernio Statio Quinctio</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Macedoni Quinctiano consuli</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">sodali <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustali</ex></expan> curatori viae Appia</supplied>e <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">et <expan><abbr>alimentor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> legato legioni</supplied>s X <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">geminae <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> comiti divi Hadri</supplied>ani <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">per Orientem et <expan><abbr>Illyr</abbr><ex>icum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praet</abbr><ex>ori</ex></expan> i</supplied>nter <supplied reason="lost">cives et <expan><abbr>peregr</abbr><ex>inos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uno</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pl</abbr><ex>ebis</ex></expan> can</supplied><expan><abbr>didat</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">comiti per <expan><abbr>Sicil</abbr><ex>iam</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Afric</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> Mauret</supplied>aniam <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">quaestori <expan><abbr>candid</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uno</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>latic</abbr><ex>lavio</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>legion</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">XXX Ulpiae victricis triumviro</supplied> aere au<lb break="no" n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">ro argento flando feriundo <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ergänzung anhand zweier weiterer Ehreninschriften für den Senator aus Aquileia (AE 1957, 135, CIl V 865). Datierung: nicht vor 138 n. Chr., als der Geehrte wohl Suffektkonsul war.</p>
